        "id": 5561,
        "name": "A.J. Beamon",
        "username": "ajbeamon",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/ajbeamon/{size}/13_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-11-14T20:46:22.590Z",
        "cooked": "<p>You can configure the retry behavior by setting a <a href=\"https://godoc.org/github.com/apple/foundationdb/bindings/go/src/fdb#TransactionOptions.SetRetryLimit\">retry limit</a> or <a href=\"https://godoc.org/github.com/apple/foundationdb/bindings/go/src/fdb#TransactionOptions.SetTimeout\">timeout</a> on the transaction or as a <a href=\"https://godoc.org/github.com/apple/foundationdb/bindings/go/src/fdb#DatabaseOptions.SetTransactionRetryLimit\">database default</a>.</p>\n<p>With a retry limit, the transaction will fail with the last error if it wants to retry but has met the limit. With a timeout, you will get a timeout error if the transaction takes longer than the specified duration.</p>",
        "post_number": 2,
        "post_type": 1,
